# Steps to Install SASS on Windows

1. I Opened Command Prompt or PowerShell or git bash

2. I Navigated to my project repository:
   cd alx-intermediate-frontend

3. I Created a new directory for the SASS project:
   mkdir 0x03-sass_scss
   cd 0x03-sass_scss

4. I already Installed Node.js

5. I Verified the installation:
   node -v
   npm -v

6. Installed SASS using npm:
   npm install sass -v 3.7.4

7. Verified SASS installation:
   npx sass --version
